ActBoards of Trade Act
SubjectChambre de commerce du Haut-Saint-François (Quebec) ** Change of Boundaries **
PrecisOrder approving the application by the CHAMBRE DE COMMERCE DU HAUT-SAINT-FRANÇOIS, in Quebec, TO CHANGE THE BOUNDARIES OF ITS DISTRICT from the municipalities of Ascot Corner, Bury, Chartierville, Cookshire-Eaton, East-Angus, Hampden, La Patrie, Newport, Scotstown, Saint-Isidore-de-Clifton and the Township of Westbury to Ascot Corner, Bury, Chartierville, Cookshire-Eaton, East Angus, Hampden, La Patrie, Newport, Saint-Isidore-de-Clifton, Scotstown, Westbury, Dudswell, Lingwick and Weedon.
